Invocation Name: visit days
des: Your digital assistant to VisitDays, with valuable insights to your visits to better engage with student visitors! You can find out about how many students are coming today or in the future; whether you may need to cancel because of impending weather, or if you want to know how your teams are performing. Requires use of VisitDays.
